    {
      "id": "593c116e-de65-4f5b-8312-dfd9326fab2d",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors use a semi supervised topic modelling approach to classify educational videos. Idea is to automate the process of labelling of the videos, which will make them easier to find in search or recommender systems. Results show that approach proposed with this method beats other alternatives. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "593c116e-de65-4f5b-8312-dfd9326fab2d",
